(this["webpackJsonpzume-pwa"]=this["webpackJsonpzume-pwa"]||[]).push([[3],{473:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"t":"Session 3","assets":[{"type":"video","key":"spiritual-economy"},{"type":"video","key":"the-gospel"},{"type":"audio","key":"baptism"}],"sections":[{"t":"LOOKING BACK","parts":[{"t":"CHECK-IN","d":["Before getting started, take some time to check-in.","At the end of the last session, everyone in your group was challenged in two ways:",["You were asked to pray for five people from your List of 100 that you marked as an \\"Unbeliever\\" or \\"Unknown.\\"","You were encouraged to share how to make a List of 100 with someone."],"Take a few moments to see how your group did this week."]},{"t":"PRAY","d":"Pray and thank God for the results and invite His Holy Spirit to lead your time together."},{"t":"OVERVIEW","d":["In this session, you\u2019ll learn how God\u2019s Spiritual Economy works and how God invests more in those who are faithful with what they\'ve already been given. You\'ll also learn two more tools for making disciples \u2013 sharing God\u2019s Story from Creation to Judgement and Baptism.","Then, when you\'re ready, get started!"]}]},{"t":"The Kingdom Economy","d":"Learn how God\'s economy is different from the world\'s. God invests more in those who are faithful with what they\'ve already been given.","duration":15,"parts":[{"type":"watch","d":"In this broken world, people feel rewarded when they take, when they receive and when they gain more than those around them. But God\'s Spiritual Economy is different \u2013 God invests more in those who are faithful with what they\'ve already been given.","payload":{"video":"spiritual-economy"}},{"type":"discuss","questions":["What are some differences you see between God\'s Spiritual Economy and our earthly way of getting things done?"]}]},{"t":"Read and Discuss (15min)","duration":15,"parts":[{"type":"read","d":["Jesus said, \u201cYou will receive power when the Holy Spirit comes upon you. And you will be my witnesses, telling people about me everywhere \u2013 in Jerusalem, throughout Judea, in Samaria, and to the ends of the earth.\u201d","Jesus believed in His followers so much, He trusted them to tell His story. Then He sent them around the world to do it. Now, He\u2019s sending us.","There\u2019s no one \u201cbest way\u201d to tell God\u2019s story (also called The Gospel), because the best way will depend on who you\u2019re sharing with. Every disciple should learn to tell God\u2019s Story in a way that\u2019s true to scripture and connects with the audience they\u2019re sharing with."]},{"type":"discuss","questions":["What comes to mind when you hear God\'s command to be His \\"witness\\" and to tell His story?","Why do you think Jesus\xa0chose ordinary people instead of some other way to share His Good News?","What would it take for you to feel more comfortable sharing God\'s Story?"]}]},{"t":"The Gospel and How to Share It","d":"Learn a way to share God\u2019s Good News from the beginning of humanity all the way to the end of this age.","duration":15,"parts":[{"type":"watch","d":[{"t":"The Gospel","d":"One way to share God\u2019s Good News is by telling God\u2019s Story from Creation to Judgement \u2013 from the beginning of humankind all the way to the end of this age."}],"payload":{"video":"the-gospel"}},{"type":"discuss","questions":["What do you learn about mankind from this story?","What do you learn about God?","Do you think it would be easier or harder to share God\'s Story by telling a story like this?"]}]},{"t":"PRACTICE SHARING GOD\'S STORY (45min)","duration":45,"info":"Break into groups of two or three people and spend the next 45 minutes practicing telling God\'s Story. You can use the using the Activity instructions for \\"God\'s Story\\" found in your Z\xfame Guidebook."},{"t":"Baptism and How To Do It","d":"Jesus said, \u201cGo and make disciples of all nations, BAPTIZING them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit\u2026\u201d Learn how to put this into practice.","duration":15,"parts":[{"type":"read","d":[{"t":"Baptism","d":"Jesus said, \u201cGo and make disciples of all nations, BAPTIZING them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit\u2026\u201d"}]},{"type":"listen","payload":{"audio":"baptism"}},{"type":"discuss","questions":["Have you ever baptized someone?","Would you even consider it?","If the Great Commission is for every follower of Jesus, does that mean every follower is allowed to baptize others? Why or why not?"],"info":["IMPORTANT REMINDER \u2013 Have you been baptized?","If not, then we encourage you to plan this before even one more session of this training. Invite your group to be a part of this important day when you celebrate saying \\"yes\\" to Jesus."]}]},{"t":"LOOKING FORWARD","d":"Congratulations on finishing Session 3! ","info":"Below are next steps to take in preparation for the next session.","parts":[{"t":"OBEY","d":"Spend time this week practicing God\'s Story, and then share it with at least one person from your List of 100 that you marked as \\"Unbeliever\\" or \\"Unknown.\\""},{"t":"SHARE","d":"Ask God who He wants you to train to use the Creation to Judgment story (or some other way to share God\'s Story). Share this person\'s name with the group before you go."},{"t":"PRAY","d":"Pray that God helps you be obedient to Him and invite Him to work in you and those around you!"},{"t":"#ZumeProject","d":"What\u2019s been your Z\xfame highlight? Tell others about it on social media."},{"info":"IMPORTANT REMINDER \u2013 Your group will be celebrating the Lord\'s Supper next session. Be sure to remember the supplies (bread and wine / juice)."}]}]}')}}]);
